{"tid":600797,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"科索沃反對黨　議事廳內擲催淚彈阻投票","createTime":"2018-03-21T15:42:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-21T16:11:02.000Z","uid":53379,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b86cd5bcde9c5a465bdde077e07304e8061716b4","tid":600797,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T15:42:57.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">科索沃反對黨　議事廳內擲催淚彈阻投票</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180321/s00005/d994730e05ec9a32a32bfc174c721842.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180321%2Fs00005%2Fd994730e05ec9a32a32bfc174c721842.jpg&h=f1b2275a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2008年脫離塞爾維亞獨立的科索沃，近10年政局依然動蕩不安。周三（21日），其國會在審議有關與鄰國黑山的邊境協定時，有反對黨成員在議事廳投擲催淚彈，令這個巴爾幹半島國家的前程，再度蒙上陰影。<br />\n<br />\n據報，投擲催淚彈的是科索沃反對派「自決行動黨」。他們批評與黑山的邊界協定，會使科索沃失去近80平方公里的領土，形同割地。因此他們便在議事廳施放三個催淚彈，迫使議員離開議事廳，從而令投票人數少過法定的三分之二。<br />\n<br />\n黑山與科索沃的邊界協定是由歐盟牽頭制定，科索沃可以借此協定，換取公民能在俗稱「申根區」的26個歐洲國家內，免簽證自由進出。歐盟大使和美國駐科索沃大使雙雙發表聲明，譴責反對黨有關行為，並呼籲各議員盡快返回議事廳投票，避免窒礙科索沃未來發展。<br />\n<br />\n（獨立報）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180321/s00005/1521642745532\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180321%2Fs00005%2F1521642745532&d=66jwbLEEruHbFfMAf1JUagKEmdudW1rq3V1Y15kzxIU%3D&h=aba176c3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180321%2Fs00005%2F1521642745532&h=808ca744\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180321/s00005/1521642745532</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qYPKHbs04EY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DqYPKHbs04EY&d=66jwbLEEruHbFfMAf1JUagKEmdudW1rq3V1Y15kzxIU%3D&h=665485c3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qYPKHbs04EY</a><br />\n<br 